1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
ظآزA little bit sorry for my love for youظآز

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
ظآزSorry, I was a little lateظآز

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
ظآزI really want the unconscious longing
to appear fasterظآز

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
ظآزCan I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once moreظآز

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
ظآزHolding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journeyظآز

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
ظآزThe chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after anotherظآز

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
ظآزThe promised moment
will definitely not be forgottenظآز

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
ظآزCan I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeatظآز

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
ظآزStart the countdown 4321,
a new sceneryظآز

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
ظآزI want to see all the scenes about youظآز

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
ظآزNo need to miss you anymoreظآز

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
ظآزRight by your sideظآز

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:03,136
=Episode 13=

15
00:01:05,625 --> 00:01:13,888
(Miss Jin, you've worked hard.
You can have a day off tomorrow.)

16
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,120
I got you here.

17
00:01:46,133 --> 00:01:47,399
I came back for my phone.

18
00:01:56,433 --> 00:01:58,433
Thank you. I'm leaving.

19
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,633
Wait.

20
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,376
- Anything to say?
- Anything to say?

21
00:02:15,072 --> 00:02:16,000
- No.
- No.

22
00:02:19,133 --> 00:02:20,128
Really?

23
00:02:24,733 --> 00:02:25,766
I...

24
00:02:50,496 --> 00:02:52,033
Lan Chen, who do you think you are?

25
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:54,700
Miss Jin, he's not a good person.

26
00:02:54,733 --> 00:02:55,700
What?

27
00:02:56,192 --> 00:02:57,433
Won't admit it?

28
00:02:58,300 --> 00:03:00,466
He was the one who had me corner you.

29
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,200
What did you say?

30
00:03:05,733 --> 00:03:06,533
Listen.

31
00:03:08,288 --> 00:03:10,066
A grand group CEO hired someone

32
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,733
to intimidate his secretary.

33
00:03:12,766 --> 00:03:13,566
Hmph.

34
00:03:13,933 --> 00:03:15,266
What a despicable move.

35
00:03:16,704 --> 00:03:18,333
What are you talking about?

36
00:03:18,976 --> 00:03:22,300
It's getting interesting.

37
00:03:22,848 --> 00:03:24,000
Acting now?

38
00:03:25,248 --> 00:03:26,432
Amnesia?

39
00:03:27,328 --> 00:03:29,133
The transfer record is on my phone.

40
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:33,433
Be our boss's girlfriend.

41
00:03:33,664 --> 00:03:36,576
- Be his girlfriend.
- Be his girlfriend.

42
00:03:36,576 --> 00:03:37,600
Louder.

43
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:42,975
- Be his girlfriend.
- Be his girlfriend.

44
00:03:45,088 --> 00:03:46,100
Did you hear that?

45
00:03:53,366 --> 00:03:55,033
Who's so bold?

46
00:03:56,416 --> 00:03:58,100
Daring to stir up trouble here.

47
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,300
Stop.

48
00:04:27,328 --> 00:04:28,666
Let me take you home.

49
00:04:29,696 --> 00:04:32,733
No need. I prefer riding a motorcycle.

50
00:04:34,496 --> 00:04:39,403
ظآزSnapping out of it for a second, I want
to get away from this endless messظآز

51
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:45,104
ظآزLove is like a trap,
a carefully designed illusionظآز

52
00:04:45,104 --> 00:04:50,656
ظآزWrite your name on the memories
that were once left behindظآز

53
00:04:51,102 --> 00:04:55,744
ظآزThe once fleeting joy vanishedظآز

54
00:04:57,792 --> 00:04:58,848
Miss Jin!

55
00:05:01,088 --> 00:05:06,377
ظآزLove is like a meteor, taking away
the expectations and never coming backظآز

56
00:05:06,464 --> 00:05:10,072
(Inpatient)

57
00:05:10,072 --> 00:05:11,767
ظآزIts traces are etched in my memoryظآز

58
00:05:11,767 --> 00:05:14,784
ظآزOnce again, I indulge in itظآز

59
00:05:19,266 --> 00:05:21,000
What exactly did you just say?

60
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,300
(Chat records between CFO and Ling Feng)
I told you it was Lan Chen.

61
00:05:33,632 --> 00:05:34,666
I was not lying.

62
00:05:35,266 --> 00:05:37,800
This isn't Lan Chen's WeChat.
It's the CFO's.

63
00:05:40,832 --> 00:05:42,500
Anyway, he is not a good person.

64
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:43,666
Are you?

65
00:05:43,933 --> 00:05:46,333
You took the money to corner a girl.

66
00:05:48,900 --> 00:05:50,266
Didn't I get beaten by you?

67
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:52,300
Give me the phone.

68
00:06:04,333 --> 00:06:07,066
Seems these people
have long been targeting Lan Chen.

69
00:06:07,966 --> 00:06:11,000
Now it's not just about the company.
It's personal grudges.

70
00:06:21,166 --> 00:06:22,733
Okay, I got it.

71
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:28,300
Something happened
at the gym. I gotta go.

72
00:06:32,704 --> 00:06:35,233
What do you want to eat for night snack?
I'll go buy it.

73
00:06:38,368 --> 00:06:41,200
Oh, this bracelet is pretty nice.

74
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:44,633
Be careful. I'm leaving.

75
00:06:50,466 --> 00:06:55,366
(Miss Jin, you've worked hard.
You can have a day off tomorrow.)

76
00:07:14,336 --> 00:07:15,328
Why are you here?

77
00:07:18,624 --> 00:07:20,633
I heard Mrs. Jin was hospitalized.

78
00:07:21,088 --> 00:07:22,700
Of course, I should come.

79
00:07:25,664 --> 00:07:26,800
Besides,

80
00:07:27,296 --> 00:07:29,033
the person who upset her this time

81
00:07:29,856 --> 00:07:30,933
wasn't me.

82
00:07:32,224 --> 00:07:33,472
No need.

83
00:07:33,472 --> 00:07:35,072
You're not welcome here.

84
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,933
Who would like to come here?

85
00:07:40,352 --> 00:07:41,376
Besides,

86
00:07:41,984 --> 00:07:44,266
I don't really like the smell of her.

87
00:07:44,992 --> 00:07:46,208
I won't go in.

88
00:07:48,448 --> 00:07:50,133
You'd better get out.

89
00:07:52,966 --> 00:07:53,766
Me?

90
00:07:54,848 --> 00:07:56,600
The one who should leave is you.

91
00:07:58,784 --> 00:08:00,100
Because of your antics,

92
00:08:00,448 --> 00:08:04,066
there's no way that Lan could get
investment from Lihuai International.

93
00:08:04,704 --> 00:08:05,866
Are you satisfied?

94
00:08:08,992 --> 00:08:10,899
What are you trying to say?

95
00:08:13,952 --> 00:08:17,433
I advise you to leave Lan.

96
00:08:18,048 --> 00:08:21,200
Even if I do it,
you still won't get him.

97
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,696
If I can't have him,

98
00:08:27,488 --> 00:08:29,000
I'll destroy him.

99
00:08:30,272 --> 00:08:32,100
No one can have him.

100
00:08:39,904 --> 00:08:40,800
Listen,

101
00:08:41,696 --> 00:08:43,033
you can't destroy

102
00:08:44,064 --> 00:08:45,600
my man.

103
00:09:01,248 --> 00:09:03,904
Dear journalists,
aren't you looking for Miss Jin?

104
00:09:03,904 --> 00:09:05,152
She's here.

105
00:09:23,456 --> 00:09:24,633
Why is it so noisy?

106
00:09:39,136 --> 00:09:40,096
Quiet!

107
00:09:42,624 --> 00:09:43,904
I am Miss Jin's sister.

108
00:09:48,148 --> 00:09:52,670
ظآزI pass through the crowd with youظآز

109
00:09:55,700 --> 00:10:00,661
ظآزAs if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each otherظآز

110
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:09,534
ظآزWhen the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps inظآز

111
00:10:09,534 --> 00:10:15,776
ظآزYou come with light,
shining into my heartظآز

112
00:10:16,608 --> 00:10:20,485
ظآزStars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heartظآز

113
00:10:20,485 --> 00:10:24,606
ظآزI make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting starظآز

114
00:10:24,606 --> 00:10:26,302
ظآزOpen my secretظآز

115
00:10:26,302 --> 00:10:32,350
ظآزI hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for youظآز

116
00:10:32,350 --> 00:10:36,222
ظآزSinking into your love,
I want to sink deeperظآز

117
00:10:36,222 --> 00:10:40,728
ظآزWith each breath,
I can feel the sweetnessظآز

118
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:49,438
ظآزTwo lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fateظآز
